1
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,240
Mr. Lu,

2
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:25,440
Ms. Su has already been taking a bath

3
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,500
as you instructed.

4
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:28,200
Remember,

5
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,090
in the Lu family,

6
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,080
she is not Ms. Su.

7
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,520
She doesn't deserve a title.

8
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,160
It seems Xiao Qi didn't satisfy you,

9
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,460
so you couldn't wait
to throw yourself at me.

10
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,400
What exactly do you want?

11
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,640
Don't forget what I said.

12
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:16,120
Don't lie to me.

13
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:17,560
Lu Fan,

14
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,440
what else do you want from me?

15
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:21,000
Just say it all at once.

16
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:27,920
Is it uncomfortable?

17
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,640
Does it hurt?

18
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,840
Remember this feeling.

19
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,120
Maniac.

20
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,320
It's all because of you.

21
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,360
If you dare step out of this room,

22
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,360
I will personally dig up

23
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,420
the grave of your father, Su Minghao.

24
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,960
If the stakes aren't enough,

25
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,160
I can raise them.

26
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,120
Now that I dare to come back to see you,

27
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,320
I'm not afraid of you.

28
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,280
Come at me if you have the guts.

29
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,410
Don't target my dad.

30
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,210
That depends on your performance.

31
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,440
Come here.

32
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,930
I only give you ten seconds.

33
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,250
Crawl over here.

34
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,760
Take one more step,

35
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:30,960
and I'll scatter a handful
of your father's ashes.

36
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,600
Beg me.

37
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:55,880
I beg you.

38
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:02,840
Boring.

39
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:10,120
I want to see your imploring expression.

40
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,480
Please let my father go,

41
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:20,839
Mr. Lu.

42
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,970
That's more like it.

43
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,800
Remember your place.

44
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:32,120
You're a plaything to pay
for your sister's

45
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,760
and your own sins.

46
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:38,720
Your only value is pleasing me.

47
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:43,380
It's also the only way of keeping
your father's peace after death.

48
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,540
You should think about

49
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,890
what exactly you should do.

50
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,760
Ms. Jian, Mr. Lu hasn't woken up yet.

51
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:17,880
Why don't you wait
in the living room first?

52
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:18,880
Get out of the way.

53
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:20,840
Lu Fan.

54
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:22,680
Lu Fan!

55
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,080
I'm coming in.

56
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:29,760
Oh no.

57
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,860
This is going to be explosive.

58
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,159
You're here.

59
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:40,880
Go to the dining room first.

60
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,280
I'll be there in a minute.

61
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:44,280
The shareholders are so anxious

62
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,920
that they have even called me.

63
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,580
Yet you're so relaxed, Mr. Lu.

64
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:50,520
I hope I didn't interrupt anything,
Mr. Lu.

65
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:55,400
You might have interrupted
if you came last night.

66
00:05:57,600 --> 00:06:00,530
Do you think I can't satisfy you
after we get married?

67
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:02,440
Or,

68
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:05,730
we don't even have to wait until marriage.

69
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:12,680
You will be Mrs. Lu.

70
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,980
There's no need to lower yourself

71
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:19,840
to be jealous of a plaything.

72
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:23,920
Wait a minute.

73
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,050
Where are you going?

74
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,090
Clean up the room first.

75
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,440
And,

76
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,800
don't forget our contract.

77
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,720
Without my permission,

78
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,980
you can't go anywhere.

79
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,360
Be on call.

80
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,560
I didn't hear your answer.

81
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:50,760
Okay, Mr. Lu.

82
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,680
Do you have any other orders?

83
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:01,020
To the restaurant.

84
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,080
Let's go.

85
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,080
Let's go.

86
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,880
How is your hand?

87
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,120
Dr. Li will be back soon.

88
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:25,170
It just hurts when it's cloudy or raining.

89
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:28,080
Usually it's fine.

90
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,170
The coffee is getting cold, right?

91
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,320
Su Xia,

92
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,640
add some coffee for Ms. Jian.

93
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:49,409
Hold it with your crippled right hand.

94
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,020
Aren't you good at acting?

95
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,300
Hold it steady.

96
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,320
If you spill a drop,

97
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:58,120
I'll have someone dig a shovel of

98
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,930
dirt from your father's grave.

99
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,120
Su Xia,

100
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,680
your existence is a mistake.

101
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,760
You are a burden like your father.

102
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:34,760
Lu Fan.

103
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,840
Come at me if you want revenge.

104
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,200
Don't insult my father.

105
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:43,919
Get out.

106
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,050
What's the schedule today?

107
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,880
The bidding result of the project

108
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:25,160
in the East City Development Zone is out.

109
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,090
You need to go there around 3:00 PM.

110
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,360
Okay.

111
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,620
Give me your phone.

112
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,160
Who sent you the message?

113
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,080
A friend.

114
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:54,250
Everything about you is under my control.

115
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:57,200
You are not allowed to go out today
without my permission.

116
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:57,930
Understand?

117
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,160
Understood.

118
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:03,560
Let's go.

119
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:18,160
G, Top-tier Psychological Counselor,

120
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:18,920
No, we couldn't accept the so-called
top-tier psychological counselor.

121
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:21,080
Member of
the European Psychological Association,

122
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:21,840
has won…

123
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,970
Wow, so many awards.

124
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,090
Impressive.

125
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,240
Dr. G.

126
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,690
You were always abroad before.

127
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:38,360
As an old guy,

128
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:41,040
I could only make international calls
to you.

129
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:43,200
Today, we finally meet.

130
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:47,360
You call this a meeting?

131
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:51,160
I'm really sorry.

132
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:53,200
I don't like treating patients
face-to-face,

133
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:55,200
so I choose to talk to you
from behind this curtain.

134
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,440
I hope you don't mind.

135
00:11:58,840 --> 00:11:59,770
I want to see her.

136
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,840
How do I make an appointment?

137
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:05,260
Please fill out this test form first.

138
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,720
I heard Dr. G is very mysterious.

139
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:14,520
She never shows her face in interviews.

140
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,840
But you must have seen her, right?

141
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,170
What does she look like?

142
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:20,880
Sir.

143
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:22,120
I'm sorry.

144
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,240
Dr. G

145
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,720
values her privacy.

146
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,520
So I can't tell you.

147
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,320
Then how would I know

148
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,920
if she is an imposter?

149
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:33,080
I believe when you see Dr. G,

150
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:35,140
you'll be able to judge for yourself.

151
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:35,920
All right.

152
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:46,290
If I write Lu Fan's name down

153
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,240
and the information leaks,

154
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:51,440
those reporters would make a fuss again.

155
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:53,520
No.

156
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:57,050
What happened three years ago
can't be brought up again.

157
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:58,520
Eat.

158
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:01,280
Mr. Xiao, this is raw beef, right?

159
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:10,640
This guy looks like he's sick.

160
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,840
Do you always suffer from insomnia,

161
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,920
or have poor sleep quality,

162
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,800
with heavy eye bags?

163
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:20,400
Yes.

164
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:24,000
Do you feel uncomfortable

165
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,560
when attending social occasions?

166
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:27,360
Don't like attending banquets.

167
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:27,960
Yes.

168
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:32,880
Have you lost interest in sex?

169
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,160
Sex?

170
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,050
Definitely not.

171
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,040
Okay.

172
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:40,320
Xiao,

173
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:41,960
why are you here?

174
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:42,880
Why are you here?

175
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:43,760
You freaked me out.

176
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:44,560
Are you sick?

177
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:45,760
You're the one who's sick.

178
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:47,690
Why are you here if you're not sick?

179
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:50,240
I... You scared me.

180
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:54,400
It seems like I'm the one who's sick.

181
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:55,600
No, Xiao,

182
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:56,760
listen to my excuse.

183
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:57,480
No.

184
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,160
I'd like to hear your excuse.

185
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:59,520
No, let me explain.

186
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,280
Explain.

187
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:02,480
It's like this. Well...

188
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:03,800
Well...

189
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:05,120
Well.

190
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:05,800
Xiao, here's the thing.

191
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:06,680
I made a dinner plan.

192
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:07,640
I need to head over right now.

193
00:14:07,640 --> 00:14:08,480
It's getting late.

194
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,440
So I'm in a huge hurry.

195
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,240
I have to go.

196
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:10,960
Next time,

197
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,920
I'll treat you to that raw beef.

198
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:13,520
Bye.

199
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:22,380
Mr. Xiao, you can go in now.

200
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,720
Why are you still here?

201
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,080
I... I'm sick.

202
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,410
Will you treat me or not?

203
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:36,480
I will.

204
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,280
That's right.

205
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:41,290
Fill out the form, right? Okay.

206
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:43,920
Hurry up and make an appointment.

207
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:44,880
Register for the ER.

208
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:46,000
There is no ER
in the psychology department.

209
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,600
I feel awful right now.

210
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,680
You need to treat me right away, okay?

211
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:49,800
Hurry up.
